{"tid":1821104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「街馬」10公里女冠軍好靚女","createTime":"2020-01-12T04:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T05:36:33.000Z","uid":96097,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ef74ee4c5d70fe8bb41d4d570d01660dfeff55e8","tid":1821104,"uid":96097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:22:07.000Z","msg":"「街馬」10公里女冠軍：念記香港，最重要有公義　多名跑手舉手示意毋忘「五大訴求」<br />\n<br />\n「全城街馬」今日舉行，是自反修例示威逾半年以來，首次舉行大型體育活動。女子組 10 公里賽首名衝線跑手 17 歲陳天詞說，跑步時心中念記著香港，因為社會事件並未平息，雖然有很多人執著不同政見，但最重要是有公義和愛，人人都有錯，要學識謙卑、放下自我。<br />\n<br />\n今日有跑手穿著印有「Stand With Hong Kong」、「Fight for Freedom 」等字眼的黑衣，又有人拿著「光復香港，時代革命」的標語跑步。<br />\n<br />\n多名跑手在衝線時一手舉起一指，一手舉五指，代表五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n轉：立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/街馬-多名參賽者穿-香港加油-跑衫-衝線舉手示意毋忘-五大訴求/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%A1%97%E9%A6%AC-%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%83%E8%B3%BD%E8%80%85%E7%A9%BF-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%B9-%E8%B7%91%E8%A1%AB-%E8%A1%9D%E7%B7%9A%E8%88%89%E6%89%8B%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%8F%E6%AF%8B%E5%BF%98-%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82%2F&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXfsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=df388fa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%A1%97%E9%A6%AC-%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%83%E8%B3%BD%E8%80%85%E7%A9%BF-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%B9-%E8%B7%91%E8%A1%AB-%E8%A1%9D%E7%B7%9A%E8%88%89%E6%89%8B%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%8F%E6%AF%8B%E5%BF%98-%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82%2F&h=3edb9a3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/街馬-多名參賽者穿-香港加油-跑衫-衝線舉手示意毋忘-五大訴求/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vXtFBN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vXtFBN.jpg&h=61742d4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">相由心生</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\